name: NEXT Directory
description: NEXT Directory - Powered by Hyperledger Sawtooth. NEXT is a role based access control system that supports multiple identity providers and leverages an immutable ledger for auditing purposes.  Turn your access control nightmares into an easy to maintain, self-service portal.  Slated features include configurable expiration of access, hierarchical approval options, delegation of approvals and automated renewal requests.
